# SDD Orchestrator for Codex

Spec-Driven Development workflow integrated into Codex.

## Commands
- `/sdd-init` - Initialize SDD context
- `/sdd-explore` - Investigate codebase
- `/sdd-new` - Create proposal
- `/sdd-ff` - Fast forward workflow
- `/sdd-apply` - Implement tasks
- `/sdd-verify` - Validate implementation
- `/sdd-archive` - Complete cycle